



Javascript Lang
---------------

JS lang

--> scripting lang fro web-pages in browser
+
--> server-side lang on NodeJS runtime
--> stand-alone appln
--> mobile application

-------------

JS Features

--> functional pgming lang
--> object oriented lang

--> datatypes are dynamic
--> it supports closure

--> single-threaded lang
--> will provide better concurrency

------------------------------------------


JS lang is based on 'ECMAScript' spec.

latest : ES6

-------------------------------------------

How to execute JS programs ?

 --> we need 'JS engine'

 browsers

  chrome  --> v8 ( c++ )
  firefox --> rhino ( java )
  IE      --> chakra 
  safari  --> nitro

non-browser

  node   --> v8
  JVM    --> nashorn
  MongoDB -->
  Apache CouchDB -->

  -----------------------------


  where/when i shud use JS lang ?

 --> Event-Driven , Asych processing.

